rabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011430, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah I beseech Thee that Thou, while taking decisions and rendering possible things and events decisively (decisions which cannot be changed or bypassed), write my name in the list of those pilgrims of Thy “sacred House” whose pilgrimage receives Thy approval, whose efforts are appreciated, whose sins are forgiven, whose wrongdoings are overlooked; that Thou, while making decisions and rendering possible things and events; make possible for me long life, goodness, welfare, and enough means of livelihood, and let me be like whom Thou helps with Thy Religion, not substituting any other in my place.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Jin umoor (affairs) ka Tu Lailatul Qadr mein faisla karta hai hatmi (yaqeeni) faislo’n mein se aur unko muqarrar (muqaddar) farmata hai aur jin par hikmat’e umoor mein imteyazaat (preferences) deta hai aur aisi qaza o qadr mo’ayyan karta hai jisko radd ya tabdeel nahi kiya ja sakta us mein Tu mujhe is saal ke hujjaaj (haajiyo’n) mein qaraar de, keh jin ka Hajj maqbool, jin ki saee (koshish) pasandida, jinke gunah maaf, jin ki buraaiya mita di gayi hai aur jin ka Tu ne faisla kiya us mein meri umr (life) ko daraaz (long) aur mere rizq ko wasee (ziyadah) qaraar de, aameen.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! میں تجھ سے سوال کرتا ہوں کہ تو اپنی قضا و قدر میں محکم امور سے متعلق جو یقینی فیصلے کرتا ہے جو تیری وہ قضا ہے کہ جس میں کسی بھی طرح کی ردّ وبدل نہیں ہوتی اس میں میرا نام اپنے بیت الحرام (کعبہ) کے حاجیوں میں لکھ دے کہ جن کا حج تجھے منظور ہے ان کی سعی قبول ہے ان کے گناہ بخشے گئے ہیں اور ان کی خطائیں مٹا دی گئی ہیں نیز اپنی قضا و قدر میں میری عمر طویل قرار دے جس میں بھلائی اور امن ہو میری روزی میں وسعت دے اور مجھے ان لوگوں میں قرار دے جن کے ذریعے تو اپنے دین کی مدد کرتا ہے اور میری جگہ کسی اور کو نہ دے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA INNI AS-ALOKA AN TAJ-A’LA FEE-MAA TAQZI WA TO-QADDE-RO MENAL AMRIL MAHTOO-ME FIL AMRIL HAKEEME MENAL QAZAAA-IL LAZEE LAA YO-RADDO WA LAA YO-BADDA-LO AN TAKTO-BANEE MIN HUJJAA-JE BAIYTE-KAL HARAA-MIL MAB-ROORE HAJJO-HOMUL MASH-KOORE SA’YO-HOMUL MAGH-FOORE ZONOO-BO-HOMUL MO-KAFFA-RE A’N SAYYE-AATE-HIM WA AN TAJ-A’L FEE-MAA TAQZI WA TO-QADDE-RO AN TOTEE-LA U’MREE FEE KHAI-RIN WA AA’FE-YATIN WA TO-WASSE-A’ FEE RIZQEE WA TAJ-A’L-NEE MIMMAN TAN-TASERO BEHI LE-DEENE-KA WA LAA TAS-TABDIL FEE GHAIREE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْئَلُکَ اَنْ تَجْعَلَ فِیْمَا تَقْضٖی وَتُقَدِّرُ مِنَ الْاَمْرِالْمَحْتُوْمِ فِی الْاَمْرِ الْحَکِیْمِ مِنَ الْقَضَآئِ الَّذِیْ لَایُرَدُّ وَلَا یُبَدَّلُ اَنْ تَکْتُبَنِیْ مِنْ حُجَّاجِ بَیْتِکَ الْحَرَامِ الْمَبْرُوْرِ حَجُّھُمُ الْمَشْکُوْرِ سَعْیُہُمُ الْمَغْفُوْرِ ذُنُوْبُھُمُ الْمُکَفَّرِعَنْ سَیِّئَآتِھِمْ وَاَنْ تَجْعَلَ فِیْمَا تَقْضٖی وَتُقَدِّرُ اَنْ تُطِیْلَ عُمْرِیْ فِیْ خَیْرٍ وَّعَافِیَۃٍ وَّتُوَسِّعَ فِیْ رِزْقِیْ وَتَجْعَلَنِیْ مِمَّنْ تَنْتَصِرُ بِہٖ لِدِیْنِکَ وَلَا تَسْتَبْدِلْ بِیْ غَیْرِیْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null,